<p>I think this is a fun read, and I think that the properties of particular Amnestics could add to SCPs down the road, where a poor choice of drug causes a story twist.</p>
<p>It does seem exceedingly strange, however, to restrict to the O5 council that these drugs have leaked into the general population. The fact that your second cousin Bob might be huffing lethe is a O5 council level piece of information?</p>

