														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3772416">
									

<p>This piece is fun, and will no doubt be very useful to many writers. I buy this explanation, that the 05 council simply doesn't care about civilian use; fits right in with most iterations/concepts of the 05 council.</p>
<p>However, wouldn't the 05 council/the Foundation at large be concerned that any GOI can now use these non-anomalous amnestics?</p>
<p>Additionally, I'd like some clarification on exactly which amnestics are non-anomalous, and I'm not sure how mnestics work now - are they all anomalous, and thus only accessible by the Foundation (which would solve the GOI issue somewhat), or are just some anomalous, or what?</p>
<p>+1 from me. I get excited when I see your name next to a piece, keep up the solid work.</p>

							</div>

								
					
